Future Enhancements
Social Sign-In: Integration with Google, Facebook, and Apple sign-in options.
Enhanced Security: Further security measures, such as CSRF protection and two-factor authentication.
User Profile: A user profile page where users can update their information.
Note Management: Full note-taking features, including creating, editing, and deleting notes.
Contributing
Contributions are welcome! Please fork this repository and submit a pull request for any changes you'd like to make.

